---
source: crates/daemon/tests/cli_help.rs
expression: stdout
---
List attachments for one message, or for every match of a `--search QUERY`. Multi-message output prefixes each section with `--- MESSAGE_ID ---`

Usage: mxr attachments list [OPTIONS] [MESSAGE_ID]

Arguments:
  [MESSAGE_ID]

Options:
      --search <SEARCH>
      --first
      --limit <LIMIT>
  -h, --help             Print help
